        <h2><a href="node_73.html">The Establishment Contract of the “Bebras International” Association Has Been Signed</a></h2>
    <span property="dc:title" content="Russia and Belarus suspended from the IBC" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
  <div class="clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded">
<br>
<p> On December 8th, the establishment contract of the “Bebras International” was signed at Vilnius University. “Bebras International” is an international association of organisations in the field of Informatics. Its goal is to promote computer science and computational thinking among youth, teachers, and the general public.
<a href="https://www.vu.lt/en/news-events/news/the-establishment-contract-of-the-bebras-international-association-has-been-signed?fbclid=IwAR32gh5FBgtCY5n5OdPjtG8cq14cobu261dR4qYcOrePWIdJJ-S0tzBgQcE" target="_blank">More information.</a>
<br>
<img alt="" src="sites/default/files/2023_12_08_VU_Vizitas1_web-12.jpg" style="width: 400px;" /> <img alt="" src="sites/default/files/2023-12-08_Bebras_880x586.jpg" style="width: 400px;" />
</p>
<br>
<p> Published December, 2023 </p>
</div></div></div>  </div>
	
