        <h2><a href="node_64.html">WITSA 2014 Global ICT Excellence Award for Bebras</a></h2>
    <span property="dc:title" content="WITSA 2014 Global ICT Excellence Award for Bebras" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
  <div class="clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>Very good news from WITSA 2014 Global ICT Excellence Awards. <strong style="line-height: 1.538em;">BEBRAS was selected as one of this year’s Merit Award winners.</strong></p>
<p>The award was given for its a collaborative international network to promote Informatics among primary, secondary and high school students and teachers; for attracting school age children, especially girls in science and technology, and engaging them in computer sciences, engineering and mathematics.</p>
<p> </p>
